parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery drain and failure can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery drains quickly
the vehicle stalls or fails to start
the battery needs to be replaced frequently
the vehicle's electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system malfunction can cause the vehicle's systems to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's systems malfunction
the battery drains quickly
the vehicle stalls or fails to start
the electrical system causes other components to fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake light failure can cause accidents or injuries, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's braking.
symptoms: The brake lights do not function
the brake light bulbs burn out frequently
the vehicle's brake system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The horn failure can cause accidents or injuries, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's presence.
symptoms: The horn does not function
the horn only works when the steering wheel is turned
the vehicle's electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The acceleration and surging issues can cause accidents or injuries, as the vehicle may suddenly accelerate or surge forward.
symptoms: The vehicle surges forward suddenly
the vehicle is slow to respond on acceleration
the vehicle's engine malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag and Occupant Detection System Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag and occupant detection system issues can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy properly.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the passenger airbag off indicator illuminates
the seatbelt alarm sounds when no one is sitting in the front passenger seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ODS can cause the passenger airbag to turn off, even when a passenger is sitting in the seat, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light indicates "off" even when a passenger is sitting in the seat
the SRS airbag warning light is on
and the airbag system may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor mat can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The SRS airbag warning light is on
the airbag system may not deploy in the event of an accident
and the passenger airbag light indicates "off" even when a passenger is sitting in the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the horn to malfunction, which can lead to an accident or failure to warn other drivers of a potential hazard.
symptoms: The horn does not work
and the airbag system may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The SRS airbag warning light is on
the airbag system may not deploy in the event of an accident
and the passenger airbag light indicates "off" even when a passenger is sitting in the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stuck ignition key can cause inconvenience, delay, and potentially lead to safety issues if the driver is unable to leave the vehicle or respond to an emergency situation.
symptoms: The key gets stuck in the ignition
cannot be removed from the ignition
or requires repeated attempts to remove.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power can cause accidents, especially when driving on highways or in heavy traffic, and may lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
accelerates without warning
or stalls without warning
often without any prior indication or warning lights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The weak or thin windshield can cause visibility issues, especially during night driving, rain, or snow, which can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The windshield cracks or chips easily
often without any apparent cause or warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch master cylinder or slave cylinder can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
sticks to the floor
or does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TPMS can lead to tire blowouts, accidents, and injuries, especially if the driver is not aware of the low tire pressure.
symptoms: The tire pressure warning light comes on despite correct tire pressure
and key fobs may stop working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lift gate strut can cause injury or damage, especially if the gate falls suddenly.
symptoms: The lift gate strut shears off or breaks
causing the gate to fall or crash down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the AC condenser assembly can cause the AC to malfunction, leading to discomfort and distraction while driving.
symptoms: The AC does not work properly
or the driver's side output is hot air.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the navigation/audio system can cause distraction and inconvenience, especially if the driver needs to physically look at the map display for directions.
symptoms: The audio stops providing voice directions
or the radio display locks
preventing other usage of the information screen.
